data.text: ITEM Vlll. Furthermore, I instruct that all of my sons, [Person-2], [Person-4] and [Person-6], choose in fair rotation any furniture, pictures, knickknacks and any other property not heretofore bequeathed, that they may want. I further instruct that any unclaimed balance of these items be bequeathed unto my dear friend [Person-7].

ITEM IX. I furthermore want to state to each member of my beloved family that I love you each very much and how proud I am of each of you. I want to further state how grateful I am to my son, [Person-4], for his diligence in always remembering my birthday and Mother's day, and thank him for always making me feel special.
